{
  "stem": "16930.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 397.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I got back to the state.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I've been there altogether about 27 and 1/2 years with social services in the state, city and state.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I retired at age 62 in 19-- April-- April 1991.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and so essentially, essentially I am-- as you look around, you see books, and not just books I have [?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Shoah ?] books which I read, which I bought in college for myself to study, and I'm still a student today.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I still go to classes and go to lectures, and study on my own.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- Jewish and secular, it's primarily Jewish, but also secular subjects.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and-- and also I bought a computer, which I took, for example, a couple of courses on practicing with and collecting information.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I plan to do some writing, with God's help.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and that's pretty well-- and my sister, I brought my sister to America in 1960.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she in the meantime was working as a-- as a secretary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then she joined the-- the-- the-- the-- the-- what do they call it?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- the-- the people did the-- it's private.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They have it here also.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Blue Cross-- not Blue Cross, the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She joined the Red Cross in England, got to like it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she moved, and got into nursing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She got into nursing, because of her experiences in the Red Cross, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she became a nurse in '54.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she's been a nurse ever since.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when she came, and I brought her to America, she had a-- she had a registered nurse and her you know, license, and also-- they also used to, like midwives, midwives license.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to do that in England.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she got a job immediately.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
